objects.description: [Stuxnet](https://collaborate.mitre.org/attackics/index.php/Software/S0010) will store and execute SQL code that will extract and execute Stuxnet from the saved CAB file using xp_cmdshell with the following command: set @s = ’master..xp _ cmdshell ‘’extrac32 /y “‘+@t+‘” “’+@t+‘x”‘’’; exec(@s);(Citation: Wired W32.Stuxnet Feb 2011)

external_references.description: Nicolas Falliere, Liam O Murchu, Eric Chien. (2011, February). W32.Stuxnet Dossier (Version 1.4). Retrieved September 22, 2017.
